{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_013L2o56YdngPntZW9Wrg5hq","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/tb_ota_tran.spice has been updated successfully."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"dc3cf414-60b5-4244-9a30-3b9794da6520","uuid":"a6af67ae-1139-4a20-80ac-ef564ffe8af0","timestamp":"2026-03-23T10:49:50.690Z","tool_use_result":{"filePath":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/tb_ota_tran.spice","oldString":"meas tran sr_meas MAX dvdt FROM=10u TO=40u","newString":"meas tran sr_meas MAX dvdt FROM=11u TO=35u","originalFile":"* TB03: Transient Step Response — Slew rate (large-signal)\n* 500mV step to force current-limited slewing\n.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n\nVdd vdd 0 dc 1.8\nVbn  vbn  0 dc 0.59\nVbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.88\nVbp  vbp  0 dc 0.73\nVbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.475\n\n* 500mV step: 0.5V to 1.0V at t=10us, unity-gain feedback\nVinp vinp 0 PULSE(0.5 1.0 10u 1n 1n 50u 100u)\nXota vinp vout vout vdd 0 vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\nCL vout 0 10p\n\n.tran 10n 80u\n\n.control\nrun\n\n* Compute derivative vector, then measure its max during slewing window\nlet dvdt = deriv(v(vout))\nmeas tran sr_meas MAX dvdt FROM=10u TO=40u\n\necho \"sr_meas = $&sr_meas\"\n\n* Also provide two-crossing method as backup\n* Output goes from ~0.62V to ~0.99V, so use 0.7V and 0.9V crossings\nmeas tran t_low WHEN v(vout)=0.7 RISE=1\nmeas tran t_high WHEN v(vout)=0.9 RISE=1\n\necho \"t_low = $&t_low\"\necho \"t_high = $&t_high\"\necho \"v_low = 0.7\"\necho \"v_high = 0.9\"\n\n* Also 10-90% fallback\nmeas tran v_before FIND v(vout) AT=9.9u\nmeas tran v_after FIND v(vout) AT=60u\n\nlet step = v_after - v_before\nlet v_10 = v_before + 0.1 * step\nlet v_90 = v_before + 0.9 * step\n\nmeas tran t10 WHEN v(vout)=$&v_10 RISE=1\nmeas tran t90 WHEN v(vout)=$&v_90 RISE=1\n\necho \"t10 = $&t10\"\necho \"t90 = $&t90\"\necho \"v_before = $&v_before\"\necho \"v_after = $&v_after\"\n\nquit\n.endc\n.end\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":21,"oldLines":7,"newStart":21,"newLines":7,"lines":[" "," * Compute derivative vector, then measure its max during slewing window"," let dvdt = deriv(v(vout))","-meas tran sr_meas MAX dvdt FROM=10u TO=40u","+meas tran sr_meas MAX dvdt FROM=11u TO=35u"," "," echo \"sr_meas = $&sr_meas\""," "]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
