{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_017ccE2nNpAKvNavvkCVZpxx","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_019LFWNv9E5xp5QMmG81sYcW","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/tb_ota_cmrr.spice","content":"* TB06: Common-Mode Rejection Ratio (CMRR)\n* CMRR = Adm/Acm = differential gain / common-mode gain\n* Method: tie both inputs together, apply AC, measure common-mode gain\n* Use inductor feedback to set DC operating point\n.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n\nVdd vdd 0 dc 1.8\nVbn  vbn  0 dc 0.59\nVbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.88\nVbp  vbp  0 dc 0.73\nVbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.475\n\n* Both inputs tied together with AC stimulus (common-mode)\nVcm vcm 0 dc 0.9 ac 1\n\n* DC feedback: inductor from output to vcm_node ensures DC bias\n* The OTA output feeds back to set the operating point\nLbreak vout vfb 1G\nCdc vfb 0 1\n\n* OTA with both inputs at vcm, output feeds back via inductor for DC\nXota vcm vfb vout vdd 0 vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\nCL vout 0 10p\n\n.ac dec 100 0.1 1G\n\n.control\nrun\n\n* Common-mode gain at DC (low frequency)\nmeas ac acm_dc FIND vdb(vout) AT=1\n\n* Differential gain is ~63.5 dB from gate 2\n* CMRR = Adm - Acm (both in dB)\nlet adm_dc = 63.5\nlet cmrr = adm_dc - acm_dc\n\necho \"acm_dc = $&acm_dc\"\necho \"cmrr_dc = $&cmrr\"\n\nquit\n.endc\n.end\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":339,"cache_read_input_tokens":46629,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":339},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"dc3cf414-60b5-4244-9a30-3b9794da6520","uuid":"e711c092-8154-4146-9d12-a0f4d0747ea7"}
