{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01CPj5FPKK85F2c4B9epyWDx","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→* TB06: CMRR — Common-Mode Rejection Ratio (open-loop method)\n     2→* Break loop, AC on both inputs. CMRR = Adm(dB) - Acm(dB)\n     3→.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n     4→.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n     5→\n     6→Vdd vdd 0 dc 1.8\n     7→Vbn  vbn  0 dc 0.59\n     8→Vbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.88\n     9→Vbp  vbp  0 dc 0.73\n    10→Vbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.475\n    11→\n    12→* AC on vinp\n    13→Vinp vinp 0 dc 0.9 ac 1\n    14→\n    15→* Loop-breaking: inductor sets DC op point, Cdc blocks AC for vinn\n    16→Lbreak vout vinn_dc 1G\n    17→Cdc vinn_dc 0 1\n    18→\n    19→* AC injection on vinn: voltage source in series adds AC=1\n    20→* vinn = vinn_dc (DC from loop) + AC=1 (common-mode stimulus)\n    21→Vinn_ac vinn_dc vinn dc 0 ac 1\n    22→\n    23→Xota vinp vinn vout vdd 0 vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\n    24→CL vout 0 10p\n    25→\n    26→.ac dec 100 0.1 1Meg\n    27→\n    28→.control\n    29→run\n    30→\n    31→* Acm = common-mode gain at DC (use 1 Hz as proxy)\n    32→meas ac acm_1hz FIND vdb(vout) AT=1\n    33→\n    34→* CMRR = Adm - Acm (in dB). Adm ≈ 63.5 dB from Gate 2\n    35→let cmrr = 63.5 - acm_1hz\n    36→\n    37→echo \"cmrr_dc = $&cmrr\"\n    38→\n    39→quit\n    40→.endc\n    41→.end\n    42→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"dc3cf414-60b5-4244-9a30-3b9794da6520","uuid":"bd352413-dea4-4194-8092-d20e7f0acd79","timestamp":"2026-03-23T10:50:36.889Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/tb_ota_cmrr.spice","content":"* TB06: CMRR — Common-Mode Rejection Ratio (open-loop method)\n* Break loop, AC on both inputs. CMRR = Adm(dB) - Acm(dB)\n.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n\nVdd vdd 0 dc 1.8\nVbn  vbn  0 dc 0.59\nVbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.88\nVbp  vbp  0 dc 0.73\nVbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.475\n\n* AC on vinp\nVinp vinp 0 dc 0.9 ac 1\n\n* Loop-breaking: inductor sets DC op point, Cdc blocks AC for vinn\nLbreak vout vinn_dc 1G\nCdc vinn_dc 0 1\n\n* AC injection on vinn: voltage source in series adds AC=1\n* vinn = vinn_dc (DC from loop) + AC=1 (common-mode stimulus)\nVinn_ac vinn_dc vinn dc 0 ac 1\n\nXota vinp vinn vout vdd 0 vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\nCL vout 0 10p\n\n.ac dec 100 0.1 1Meg\n\n.control\nrun\n\n* Acm = common-mode gain at DC (use 1 Hz as proxy)\nmeas ac acm_1hz FIND vdb(vout) AT=1\n\n* CMRR = Adm - Acm (in dB). Adm ≈ 63.5 dB from Gate 2\nlet cmrr = 63.5 - acm_1hz\n\necho \"cmrr_dc = $&cmrr\"\n\nquit\n.endc\n.end\n","numLines":42,"startLine":1,"totalLines":42}}}
