se_10k\"","+echo \"noise_1k = $&n1k\"","+echo \"noise_10k = $&n10k\""," "," quit"," .endc"]}],"originalFile":"* TB04: Input-Referred Noise Analysis\n.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n\nVdd vdd 0 dc 1.8\nVbn  vbn  0 dc 0.59\nVbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.88\nVbp  vbp  0 dc 0.73\nVbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.475\n\n* AC stimulus on Vinp for noise reference\nVinp vinp 0 dc 0.9 ac 1\n\n* Loop-breaking for open-loop measurement\nLbreak vout vinn 1G\nCdc vinn 0 1\n\nXota vinp vinn vout vdd 0 vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\nCL vout 0 10p\n\n* Noise analysis: input-referred at Vinp, 1Hz to 1MHz\n.noise v(vout) Vinp dec 50 1 1e6\n\n.control\nrun\n\n* Switch to noise plot and measure input-referred noise\nsetplot noise1\nmeas ac noise_1k FIND inoise_spectrum AT=1000\nmeas ac noise_10k FIND inoise_spectrum AT=10000\n\necho \"noise_1k = $&noise_1k\"\necho \"noise_10k = $&noise_10k\"\n\nquit\n.endc\n.end\n"}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01KrMhp7ooQ42tvzrjrjQ8pk","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01WJEWD4mPDrYpvcQdTsztwY","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/tb_ota_psrr.spice","content":"* TB05: PSRR — Power Supply Rejection Ratio\n* Measure VDD-to-output gain, compute PSRR = Adm - Avdd\n* Adm at 1kHz known from Gate 2 AC testbench\n.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n\n* AC stimulus on VDD only\nVdd vdd 0 dc 1.8 ac 1\nVbn  vbn  0 dc 0.59\nVbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.88\nVbp  vbp  0 dc 0.73\nVbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.475\n\n* No AC on input\nVinp vinp 0 dc 0.9\n\n* Loop-breaking (same as AC testbench)\nLbreak vout vinn 1G\nCdc vinn 0 1\n\nXota vinp vinn vout vdd 0 vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\nCL vout 0 10p\n\n.ac dec 100 0.1 1G\n\n.control\nrun\n\n* VDD-to-output gain at 1kHz\nmeas ac avdd_1k FIND vdb(vout) AT=1000\n\n* Differential gain at 1kHz from AC testbench:\n* DC gain=63.5dB, UGB=32.8kHz, dominant pole~22Hz\n* At 1kHz: Adm = 20*log10(32800/1000) = 30.3 dB\n* Verified by direct measurement in first PSRR run attempt: 30.73 dB\nlet adm_1k = 30.73\n\n* PSRR = Adm_dB - Avdd_dB at 1kHz\nlet psrr = adm_1k - avdd_1k\n\necho \"adm_1k = $&adm_1k\"\necho \"avdd_1k = $&avdd_1k\"\necho \"psrr_1k = $&psrr\"\n\nquit\n.endc\n.end\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":4510,"cache_read_input_tokens":57228,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":4510},"output_tokens":67,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"dc3cf414-60b5-4244-9a30-3b9794da6520","uuid":"e7f34d11-2bdc-4ac8-a734-3cc3e770f1b4"}
