{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01XCs65BshPuBcEq3pLmg1M5","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good progress! Gates 1-3 pass, PSRR passes (70.5 dB). But noise and CMRR still fail.\n\n- **Noise**: dropped from 923→448 nV/rtHz at 1kHz (need <200), and 427→287 at 10kHz (need <100). The long-L NMOS helped but not enough.\n- **CMRR**: only 38.9 dB (need 60). The long-L M11 alone isn't sufficient.\n\nI need more aggressive changes. Let me analyze what's left to do:\n\n1. **Noise**: M7/M8 at L=14u reduced noise 2x but need 4.5x more. Need even longer L or larger area.\n2. **CMRR**: Need ~21 dB more. Must find a way to cascode or dramatically increase tail impedance.\n\nLet me try a different approach for the tail cascode — use vbn as the cascode gate (lower voltage)."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1962,"cache_read_input_tokens":117120,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1962},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"dc3cf414-60b5-4244-9a30-3b9794da6520","uuid":"62448b48-5961-4cf6-a7cc-a7fcf9dccaa6"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01XCs65BshPuBcEq3pLmg1M5","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01QMfk4A9HQK7VcitwCCjhqB","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"# Test tail cascode with vbn as gate bias (lower voltage)\ncat > /tmp/tb_cascode_test.spice << 'EOF'\n.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\nVdd vdd 0 dc 1.8\nVbn  vbn  0 dc 0.65\nVbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.88\nVbp  vbp  0 dc 0.73\nVbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.475\nVinp vinp 0 dc 0.9\nVinn vinn 0 dc 0.9\nXota vinp vinn vout vdd 0 vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\nCL vout 0 10p\nRbias1 vout vmid 1e6\nRbias2 xota.cas_p vmid 1e6\nVmid vmid 0 dc 0.9\n.nodeset v(vout)=0.9 v(xota.cas_p)=0.9\n.op\n.control\nrun\necho \"vtail = $&v(xota.tail)\"\necho \"m11_vds = $&@m.xota.xm11.msky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8[vds]\"\necho \"m11_vdsat = $&@m.xota.xm11.msky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8[vdsat]\"\nquit\n.endc\n.end\nEOF\n/usr/bin/ngspice -b /tmp/tb_cascode_test.spice 2>&1 | grep -E \"vtail|m11\"","description":"Check available tail headroom","timeout":120000},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1962,"cache_read_input_tokens":117120,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1962},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"dc3cf414-60b5-4244-9a30-3b9794da6520","uuid":"38198619-cdae-4e49-8c76-0384779a8dad"}
