{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01BatphHf6VG3XvLT2wdBrzE","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01J8bFFNVkCUBZyFA1yW4kze","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/tb_ota_cmrr.spice","content":"* TB06: CMRR — Common-Mode Rejection Ratio\n* Direct-input method: both inputs tied to same AC source\n* CMRR = Adm_dB - Acm_dB at DC\n.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n\nVdd vdd 0 dc 1.8\nVbn  vbn  0 dc 0.65\nVbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.88\nVbp  vbp  0 dc 0.73\nVbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.475\n\n* Both inputs tied together — pure common-mode stimulus\nVcm_p vinp 0 dc 0.9 ac 1\nVcm_n vinn 0 dc 0.9 ac 1\n\nXota vinp vinn vout vdd 0 vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\nCL vout 0 10p\n\n* DC operating point set by circuit symmetry\n.nodeset v(vout)=0.9\n\n.ac dec 100 0.1 1G\n\n.control\nrun\n\n* Common-mode gain at DC (1Hz proxy)\nmeas ac acm_dc FIND vdb(vout) AT=1\n\n* Differential gain from Gate 2: ~65 dB (conservative)\n* CMRR = Adm - Acm (both in dB)\nlet adm_dc = 65.0\nlet cmrr = adm_dc - acm_dc\n\necho \"acm_dc = $&acm_dc\"\necho \"cmrr_dc = $&cmrr\"\n\nquit\n.endc\n.end\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":236,"cache_read_input_tokens":194362,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":236},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"dc3cf414-60b5-4244-9a30-3b9794da6520","uuid":"334d575c-0fac-48f4-9bfa-51456b230a18"}
