{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01K1tSTrH5rFbGtbVgKJHoBp","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01BUoGVP6vVR9JdufYsEbNXV","name":"Agent","input":{"description":"Create corner/temp testbenches","prompt":"Create the following SPICE testbench files in /home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/. Each is a copy of tb_ota_ac.spice but with the .lib line changed for corners, or .temp added for temperature.\n\nRead tb_ota_ac.spice first to get the template. Then create these files:\n\n1. tb_corner_tt.spice - uses `.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt`\n2. tb_corner_ss.spice - uses `.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" ss`\n3. tb_corner_ff.spice - uses `.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" ff`\n4. tb_corner_sf.spice - uses `.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" sf`\n5. tb_corner_fs.spice - uses `.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" fs`\n\n6. tb_temp_-40.spice - uses tt corner, adds `.temp -40`\n7. tb_temp_27.spice - uses tt corner, adds `.temp 27`\n8. tb_temp_85.spice - uses tt corner, adds `.temp 85`\n\nEach file must output \"gain_peak\" (or \"gain_db\") and \"ugb\" measurements, same as tb_ota_ac.spice.\n\nIMPORTANT: The bias voltage Vbn should be 0.65 (same as tb_ota_ac.spice currently has).\n\nFor corner files: just change the .lib corner name.\nFor temperature files: keep tt corner and add .temp line right after .include.\n\nWrite each file using the Write tool."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1558,"cache_read_input_tokens":203150,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1558},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"dc3cf414-60b5-4244-9a30-3b9794da6520","uuid":"52eb19b6-2ded-45bb-8287-1ccad5f67c8e"}
