{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01TmuukZYekSoBwkGSBbFw1f","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→* TB01: AC Open-Loop Analysis\n     2→* Uses loop-breaking inductor technique\n     3→.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n     4→.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n     5→\n     6→.param vdd_val = 1.8\n     7→.param vcm_val = 0.9\n     8→\n     9→Vdd vdd 0 dc {vdd_val}\n    10→\n    11→* Bias voltages\n    12→Vbn  vbn  0 dc 0.65\n    13→Vbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.88\n    14→Vbp  vbp  0 dc 0.73\n    15→Vbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.475\n    16→\n    17→* Input with AC stimulus\n    18→Vinp vinp 0 dc {vcm_val} ac 1\n    19→\n    20→* Loop-breaking: L=1GH passes DC, blocks AC. C holds vinn at DC for AC.\n    21→Lbreak vout vinn 1G\n    22→Cdc vinn 0 1\n    23→\n    24→* OTA\n    25→Xota vinp vinn vout vdd 0 vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\n    26→CL vout 0 10p\n    27→\n    28→.ac dec 100 0.1 1G\n    29→\n    30→.control\n    31→run\n    32→\n    33→* Compute measurements manually and echo in format verifier expects\n    34→* Note: vp() returns RADIANS in ngspice 42, verifier expects DEGREES\n    35→\n    36→* Peak gain\n    37→meas ac gain_peak_raw MAX vdb(vout)\n    38→\n    39→* Gain at specific frequencies\n    40→meas ac g1_raw FIND vdb(vout) AT=1\n    41→meas ac g10_raw FIND vdb(vout) AT=10\n    42→meas ac g100_raw FIND vdb(vout) AT=100\n    43→\n    44→* UGB and phase at UGB\n    45→meas ac ugb_raw WHEN vdb(vout)=0 FALL=1\n    46→meas ac phase_ugb_rad FIND vp(vout) WHEN vdb(vout)=0 FALL=1\n    47→\n    48→* Convert radians to degrees for the verifier\n    49→let phase_ugb_deg = phase_ugb_rad * 180 / 3.14159265359\n    50→\n    51→* Echo results in the exact format the verifier's parse_meas expects\n    52→echo \"gain_peak = $&gain_peak_raw\"\n    53→echo \"g1 = $&g1_raw\"\n    54→echo \"g10 = $&g10_raw\"\n    55→echo \"g100 = $&g100_raw\"\n    56→echo \"ugb = $&ugb_raw\"\n    57→echo \"phase_ugb = $&phase_ugb_deg\"\n    58→\n    59→quit\n    60→.endc\n    61→.end\n    62→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01BUoGVP6vVR9JdufYsEbNXV","session_id":"dc3cf414-60b5-4244-9a30-3b9794da6520","uuid":"daee2b0d-d4ae-40af-8831-56e06ad400d0","timestamp":"2026-03-23T11:30:41.453Z"}
{"type":"system","subtype":"task_progress","task_id":"adcd40051cbdf001b","tool_use_id":"toolu_01BUoGVP6vVR9JdufYsEbNXV","description":"Writing tb_corner_tt.spice","usage":{"total_tokens":9942,"tool_uses":2,"duration_ms":11844},"last_tool_name":"Write","uuid":"bc28c4f2-e0e5-4cf4-9a38-3c6c650d042f","session_id":"dc3cf414-60b5-4244-9a30-3b9794da6520"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_013eMnWZwYMQB5HAE1szuBzF","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_019nGkAQWons9UWeTbNJDHhQ","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/tb_corner_tt.spice","content":"* TB: AC Open-Loop Analysis - TT Corner\n* Uses loop-breaking inductor technique\n.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n\n.param vdd_val = 1.8\n.param vcm_val = 0.9\n\nVdd vdd 0 dc {vdd_val}\n\n* Bias voltages\nVbn  vbn  0 dc 0.65\nVbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.88\nVbp  vbp  0 dc 0.73\nVbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.475\n\n* Input with AC stimulus\nVinp vinp 0 dc {vcm_val} ac 1\n\n* Loop-breaking: L=1GH passes DC, blocks AC. C holds vinn at DC for AC.\nLbreak vout vinn 1G\nCdc vinn 0 1\n\n* OTA\nXota vinp vinn vout vdd 0 vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\nCL vout 0 10p\n\n.ac dec 100 0.1 1G\n\n.control\nrun\n\n* Compute measurements manually and echo in format verifier expects\n* Note: vp() returns RADIANS in ngspice 42, verifier expects DEGREES\n\n* Peak gain\nmeas ac gain_peak_raw MAX vdb(vout)\n\n* Gain at specific frequencies\nmeas ac g1_raw FIND vdb(vout) AT=1\nmeas ac g10_raw FIND vdb(vout) AT=10\nmeas ac g100_raw FIND vdb(vout) AT=100\n\n* UGB and phase at UGB\nmeas ac ugb_raw WHEN vdb(vout)=0 FALL=1\nmeas ac phase_ugb_rad FIND vp(vout) WHEN vdb(vout)=0 FALL=1\n\n* Convert radians to degrees for the verifier\nlet phase_ugb_deg = phase_ugb_rad * 180 / 3.14159265359\n\n* Echo results in the exact format the verifier's parse_meas expects\necho \"gain_peak = $&gain_peak_raw\"\necho \"g1 = $&g1_raw\"\necho \"g10 = $&g10_raw\"\necho \"g100 = $&g100_raw\"\necho \"ugb = $&ugb_raw\"\necho \"phase_ugb = $&phase_ugb_deg\"\n\nquit\n.endc\n.end\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1008,"cache_read_input_tokens":8923,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1008,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":3,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01BUoGVP6vVR9JdufYsEbNXV","session_id":"dc3cf414-60b5-4244-9a30-3b9794da6520","uuid":"d5fcab6c-2f9c-40d3-ac14-b0f044bfa820"}
