{"type":"system","subtype":"task_progress","task_id":"adcd40051cbdf001b","tool_use_id":"toolu_01BUoGVP6vVR9JdufYsEbNXV","description":"Writing tb_corner_tt.spice","usage":{"total_tokens":20467,"tool_uses":18,"duration_ms":69928},"last_tool_name":"Write","uuid":"7317910e-bbec-46ec-b0d1-bccb8df653b1","session_id":"dc3cf414-60b5-4244-9a30-3b9794da6520"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01LsdjXwfe9GtfS2yrn5NfmU","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01B8wGKTTgjwVVGtyoZbVGwb","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/tb_corner_tt.spice","content":"* TB: AC Open-Loop Analysis - TT Corner\n* Uses loop-breaking inductor technique\n.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n\n.param vdd_val = 1.8\n.param vcm_val = 0.9\n\nVdd vdd 0 dc {vdd_val}\n\n* Bias voltages\nVbn  vbn  0 dc 0.65\nVbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.88\nVbp  vbp  0 dc 0.73\nVbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.475\n\n* Input with AC stimulus\nVinp vinp 0 dc {vcm_val} ac 1\n\n* Loop-breaking: L=1GH passes DC, blocks AC. C holds vinn at DC for AC.\nLbreak vout vinn 1G\nCdc vinn 0 1\n\n* OTA\nXota vinp vinn vout vdd 0 vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\nCL vout 0 10p\n\n.ac dec 100 0.1 1G\n\n.control\nrun\n\n* Compute measurements manually and echo in format verifier expects\n* Note: vp() returns RADIANS in ngspice 42, verifier expects DEGREES\n\n* Peak gain\nmeas ac gain_peak_raw MAX vdb(vout)\n\n* Gain at specific frequencies\nmeas ac g1_raw FIND vdb(vout) AT=1\nmeas ac g10_raw FIND vdb(vout) AT=10\nmeas ac g100_raw FIND vdb(vout) AT=100\n\n* UGB and phase at UGB\nmeas ac ugb_raw WHEN vdb(vout)=0 FALL=1\nmeas ac phase_ugb_rad FIND vp(vout) WHEN vdb(vout)=0 FALL=1\n\n* Convert radians to degrees for the verifier\nlet phase_ugb_deg = phase_ugb_rad * 180 / 3.14159265359\n\n* Echo results in the exact format the verifier's parse_meas expects\necho \"gain_peak = $&gain_peak_raw\"\necho \"g1 = $&g1_raw\"\necho \"g10 = $&g10_raw\"\necho \"g100 = $&g100_raw\"\necho \"ugb = $&ugb_raw\"\necho \"phase_ugb = $&phase_ugb_deg\"\n\nquit\n.endc\n.end\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":4181,"cache_read_input_tokens":16243,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":4181,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01BUoGVP6vVR9JdufYsEbNXV","session_id":"dc3cf414-60b5-4244-9a30-3b9794da6520","uuid":"1a9cbdd2-59db-4de7-ad24-696a18a862b3"}
