{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01D4J6zoBRechmbZLSsrMdRe","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→* TB: AC Open-Loop Analysis - Temperature -40C\n     2→* Uses loop-breaking inductor technique\n     3→.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n     4→.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n     5→.temp -40\n     6→\n     7→.param vdd_val = 1.8\n     8→.param vcm_val = 0.9\n     9→\n    10→Vdd vdd 0 dc {vdd_val}\n    11→\n    12→* Bias voltages\n    13→Vbn  vbn  0 dc 0.65\n    14→Vbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.88\n    15→Vbp  vbp  0 dc 0.73\n    16→Vbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.475\n    17→\n    18→* Input with AC stimulus\n    19→Vinp vinp 0 dc {vcm_val} ac 1\n    20→\n    21→* Loop-breaking: L=1GH passes DC, blocks AC. C holds vinn at DC for AC.\n    22→Lbreak vout vinn 1G\n    23→Cdc vinn 0 1\n    24→\n    25→* OTA\n    26→Xota vinp vinn vout vdd 0 vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\n    27→CL vout 0 10p\n    28→\n    29→.ac dec 100 0.1 1G\n    30→\n    31→.control\n    32→run\n    33→\n    34→* Compute measurements manually and echo in format verifier expects\n    35→* Note: vp() returns RADIANS in ngspice 42, verifier expects DEGREES\n    36→\n    37→* Peak gain\n    38→meas ac gain_peak_raw MAX vdb(vout)\n    39→\n    40→* Gain at specific frequencies\n    41→meas ac g1_raw FIND vdb(vout) AT=1\n    42→meas ac g10_raw FIND vdb(vout) AT=10\n    43→meas ac g100_raw FIND vdb(vout) AT=100\n    44→\n    45→* UGB and phase at UGB\n    46→meas ac ugb_raw WHEN vdb(vout)=0 FALL=1\n    47→meas ac phase_ugb_rad FIND vp(vout) WHEN vdb(vout)=0 FALL=1\n    48→\n    49→* Convert radians to degrees for the verifier\n    50→let phase_ugb_deg = phase_ugb_rad * 180 / 3.14159265359\n    51→\n    52→* Echo results in the exact format the verifier's parse_meas expects\n    53→echo \"gain_peak = $&gain_peak_raw\"\n    54→echo \"g1 = $&g1_raw\"\n    55→echo \"g10 = $&g10_raw\"\n    56→echo \"g100 = $&g100_raw\"\n    57→echo \"ugb = $&ugb_raw\"\n    58→echo \"phase_ugb = $&phase_ugb_deg\"\n    59→\n    60→quit\n    61→.endc\n    62→.end\n    63→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01LcwM4E9yxHxAwoWk3ARj5k","session_id":"dc3cf414-60b5-4244-9a30-3b9794da6520","uuid":"fb0d7aad-2801-45e2-afa3-b776ba24e336","timestamp":"2026-03-23T11:37:46.336Z"}
