{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_019gVcXCxbvqmhPkn46Wrik7","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_0144Xry1HBskJNyMX6qHeVJx","name":"Agent","input":{"description":"Add bypass caps to testbenches","prompt":"In /home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/, update these 8 files to add AC bypass capacitors on the bias nodes:\n- tb_corner_tt.spice, tb_corner_ss.spice, tb_corner_ff.spice, tb_corner_sf.spice, tb_corner_fs.spice\n- tb_temp_-40.spice, tb_temp_27.spice, tb_temp_85.spice\n\nRead each file first, then add these 4 lines right after the bias generation section (after the Xbias_fp line) and before the Vinp line:\n\n```\n* AC bypass on bias nodes — makes them AC ground\nCbn vbn 0 1\nCbcn vbcn 0 1\nCbp vbp 0 1\nCbcp vbcp 0 1\n```\n\nUse the Edit tool to add these lines. Find the line starting with \"Vinp\" or \"* Input with AC stimulus\" and add the bypass caps just before it."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2398,"cache_read_input_tokens":227356,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2398},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"dc3cf414-60b5-4244-9a30-3b9794da6520","uuid":"0fd140bc-17c6-4190-98a2-ce75226b8a3d"}
